          - rid: 107151343762276442
          output: 'With a hastily written missive, you mobilize the local watch.
            The Captain is displeased to follow your commands, but he knows you have
            friends in high places. Under the capable hands of the Guard, the Overseer
            saves both his foundry and his men. They know we are truly responsible
            for their salvation and choose to affiliate themselves immediately, offering
            an early tithe as thanks.

            [Gained 30 Flock & 20 Wealth]

